1. Svi smo zbunjeni tražili* sekundi* da se snađemo. (We were all confused, searching for a moment to figure out.)
2. U trenutku smo znali da je nastupilo* sekundi* dokazivanja. (At that moment we knew that the moment of proving had come.)
3. Pre nego što je prošlo* sekundi*, već smo krenuli. (Before the second had passed, we had already started.)
4. Prvo je prošla* sekundi*, a onda je usledio aplauz. (The second passed first, and then the applause followed.)
5. Nećeš verovati šta se desilo u roku od* sekundi*. (You won't believe what happened within a second.)